to create a tnf2 server you need to do the following

make a cronjob that runs the execute turn command
make a .forward file that routes incomming email to the orders

you must have java installed, put a link to the "java" in your bin directory

?set TNF2DATADIR
?set TNF2BINDIR

change $tnf2root in all ".sh" files in bin directory
change email address in Config.gml file in data directory

in game settings -
 change settings in Config.gml file and other Data*.gml files in data directory


